

<style>
.slack-container {
  height: 100vh;
}
.person, .channel {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}

.person span, .channel span {
  opacity: .5;
}
.channel i {
  font-size: 14px;
  margin-right: 4px;
}

.channel.active span {
  opacity: 1;
}

.online-badge {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background-color: #1FE5BD;
  margin-top: 2px;
  margin-right: 8px;
}


.offline-badge {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background-color: white;
  margin-top: 2px;
  margin-right: 8px;
  opacity: .5;
}
.chat-container {
  flex-grow: 1;
  padding: 16px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.chat-header {
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(240,240,240);
}

.chat-header h1 {
  font-size: 24px;
  color: #8C1BA8;
}

.chat-header i {
  font-size: 20px;
}

.chat-conversations {
  flex-grow: 1;
  padding: 16px 0;
}
.message {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.message img {
  width: 40px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  margin-right: 16px;
}

.message .message-content {
  flex-grow: 1;
}

.message .message-content p:first-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
  margin-top: 0;
  color: #8C1BA8;
}
.organizations-sidebar {
  background-color: #8C1BA8;
  color: #8C1BA8;
  padding: 16px;
  text-align: center;
}

.organization {
  opacity: .3;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 18px;
}

.organization:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

.organization.active {
  opacity: 1;
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  padding: 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

.conversations-sidebar {
  background-color: #8C1BA8;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px;
  width: 200px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.conversations-sidebar h1 {
  font-size: 24px;
}

.chat-section {
  margin-top: 24px;
}

.chat-section-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}

.chat-section-header h3 {
  font-size: 16px;
  margin: 0;
}

.form-mobile {
  transform: translateX(-100%);
  position: fixed;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(.76,.02,.5,1.01);
}
.form-mobile.displayed {
  transform: translateX(0);
}


</style>



<div class="d-flex slack-container">
  <div class="d-block d-sm-none h-100">
    <div class="form-mobile h-100">
      <%= render 'advice_form' %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="d-none d-sm-block h-100">
    <%= render 'advice_form' %>
  </div>
  <div class="chat-container">
    <div class="chat-header">
      <h1><i class="fab fa-slack-hash"></i> school closures <i class="fas fa-toggle-off d-sm-none" id="toggle"></i></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="chat-conversations">
      <div class="message">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dolzriuzv/image/upload/v1583441822/User-9_ajhycb.png" alt="">
        <div class="message-content">
          <p><strong>Fran√ßois</strong></p>
          <p>Hey everyone, is it really likely the schools will close? </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="message">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dolzriuzv/image/upload/v1583441822/User-1_v2wk46.png" alt="">
        <div class="message-content">
          <p><strong>Gurpryia</strong></p>
          <p>not sure...! </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="message">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dolzriuzv/image/upload/v1583441822/User-2_gcgdiy.png" alt="">
        <div class="message-content">
          <p><strong>Rachel</strong></p>
          <p>I think literally no one knows at this point, but it's certainly a possibility that schools are preparing for..</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="message">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dolzriuzv/image/upload/v1583441822/User-3_v9hvfb.png" alt="">
        <div class="message-content">
          <p><strong>Alexia</strong></p>
          <p>Seeing as it's happened in loads of other EU countries (those that have higher and lower numbers of cases), I think it's highly likely. And soon! Not looking forward to the quarantine kid chaos, arghhhhhhh !!!!</p>
        </div>
      </div>


    <div class="message">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dolzriuzv/image/upload/v1583441822/User-7_paahxr.png" alt="">
        <div class="message-content">
          <p><strong>Lucien</strong></p>
          <p>I think they will try and keep going till Easter or as close as possible. If the numbers rise much further I can see more people pulling their kids out.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="chat-input">
      <form action="" >
        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Type your message...">
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  const toggle = document.getElementById('toggle');
  const form = document.querySelector('.form-mobile');
  toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
    toggle.classList.toggle('fa-toggle-off');
    toggle.classList.toggle('fa-toggle-on');
    form.classList.toggle('displayed');
  });

  document.querySelector(".navbar").remove();
</script>
